flowRoot.flowPara: When the time is PM, the first circle completes, and a second one starts to cover the first. The first circle fades out to a darker color, and the new one is brighter to maintain contrast. This way the difference between AM and PM is apparent at first glance
The datepicker is a horizontal panorama.
If time selection is also needed, once the user clicks on a date, a new pane appears from the right, allowing however to go back for corrections.
